 and sample holder is investigated. The\ntotal quantum yield is split into bulk and surface contributions which are\ntested for their sensitivity to light incidence angle and polarization. Our\nresults are directly applicable to model parameters for the contact-free\ndischarge system onboard the LISA Pathfinder spacecraft.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Jun 2012 21:04:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-07-03"}
