dup obtained with the new programs, allowing a\ndecrease in execution times by an order of magnitude on modern multi-core\ncomputers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Jun 2012 22:00:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-06-08"}
